  <title>Mit dem Gegner sprechen (<cmd>say</cmd>)</title>
  <p>
    You can chat with your opponent by typing text into the
    <link xref="game-chat-concept">game chat area</link> and
    only selecting the <gui style="button">say</gui>
    button.
  </p>
  <p>
    Please note that it is not possible to talk directly
    to one of the players while <link xref="index#watching">watching</link>
    somebody else.
  </p>
